song.title: Hyped Up Space Monkeys
song.info:
Hyped Up Space Monkeys Created by Fearofdark Finished June 8th 2009
Not one of my best so far mainly cause of the sampling, but I tried going a bit experemental this time. Certainly my most abitious piece yet! Also finished in a bit of a rush, which also may explain the slightly sudden ending:P Enjoy!
